data.description: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled historic 2-story home nestled in the charming town of Cross City, Florida. This timeless residence boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 modern bathrooms, and a host of exquisite features that seamlessly blend the past with the present. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting ambiance of rich hardwood floors that flow throughout the main living areas. The kitchen, a true centerpiece of the home, showcases a stunning tile floor, an all-new stainless steel appliance package, and a farmhouse sink that adds a touch of rustic charm. The custom wood cabinetry, equipped with a soft-close feature, offers both functionality and elegance complete with a custom hood range that adds a touch of sophistication. The generously sized walk-in pantry ensures you have ample storage space for all your culinary needs. On cooler evenings, gather around the wood-burning fireplace in the living area, creating memories that will last a lifetime. Natural light streams through the new dual-pane windows, illuminating every corner of the home. Stay comfortable year-round with the 2 brand-new AC units, ensuring you can enjoy this historic gem in any season. The bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated, featuring a custom-tiled shower that adds a touch of luxury to your daily routine. In the master bedroom, you'll find a huge walk-in closet that conveniently includes a laundry room, making chores a breeze. This historic home, meticulously remodeled to modern standards, is a true testament to timeless design and functionality. Outside, the home showcases its historic charm with a beautiful front porch where you can enjoy your morning coffee or watch the world go by. The privacy-fenced backyard provides a secure space for outdoor activities and gatherings. Additionally, a 20x24 metal building offers versatile space for storage, a workshop, or any other purpose you may envision. Whether you're relaxing by the fireplace, cooking in the gourmet kitchen, or enjoying the comforts of the master suite, this Cross City treasure is ready to welcome you home!
